@startuml
!theme plain

abstract class Tool

class Atomic <<atomic / internal>> {
  write, read, parse
}

class StatefulInternal <<atomic / internal>> {
  update_context, record_metric
}

class Boundary <<atomic / boundary>> {
  invoke_llm, serve_ui
}

class Composite <<composed>> {
  generate_and_test
}

Tool <|-- Atomic
Tool <|-- StatefulInternal
Tool <|-- Boundary
Tool <|-- Composite

note bottom of Composite : anti-pattern:\ndecompose into\ntools + transitions

note bottom of Tool : classifying axes:\ninternal..boundary\nby atomic..composed
@enduml
